check if we have git
    if we don't:
        install git
    if we do: 
        continue

check if we are in a git repository
    if we are:
        check if # of args are 0:
            promt for path to push
            promt for commit message

        if # of args are 2:
                use first arg as path
                use second arg as commit message
                
        if # of args are 1:
            use first argument as commit message
        